==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*σύν / sun / soon

===Etymology===
*A primary preposition denoting union; with or together (but much closer than [[μετά]] or [[παρά]]), that is, by association, companionship, process, resemblance, possession, instrumentality, addition, etc.: 

===Preposition===
'''σύν'''

# [[beside]], [[with]]. 
*In compounds it has similar applications, including completeness.

